               <interp inst="t18450407-983" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/18450407"></interp>
               <interp inst="t18450407-983" type="date" value="18450407"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t18450407-983-charge-1" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-983-18450407 t18450407-983-offence-1 t18450407-983-verdict-1"></join>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t18450407-983-charge-2" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-983-18450407 t18450407-983-offence-1 t18450407-983-verdict-2"></join>
               <p>983. <persName id="def1-983-18450407" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def1-983-18450407" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-983-18450407" type="age" value="16"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-983-18450407" type="surname" value="SAVILLE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-983-18450407" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">WILLIAM SAVILLE</hi>
                  </persName> and <persName id="def2-983-18450407" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def2-983-18450407" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def2-983-18450407" type="age" value="16"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def2-983-18450407" type="surname" value="LEWIS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def2-983-18450407" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">ROBERT LEWIS</hi>
                  </persName> were indicted for<rs id="t18450407-983-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18450407-983-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18450407-983-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>stealing 60 yards of calico, value 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; and 1 wooden roller, 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18450407-name-1101" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1101" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1101" type="surname" value="HIGGS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1101" type="given" value="RICHARD TURNER"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18450407-983-offence-1 t18450407-name-1101"></join>Richard Turner Higgs</persName>; and that Saville had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. DOANE</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the Prosecution.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450407-name-1102" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1102" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1102" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1102" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS JONES</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Richard Turner Higgs, a draper, at Stratford. On the 28th of Feb. I placed a roll of calico on the steps inside the lobby of the door—it was on a wooden roller, and I had put a mark on it—this is the roller—(<hi rend="italic">looking at it</hi>)—I missed the calico the next morning, when Mr. Higgs told me of it—there were sixty yards of it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450407-name-1103" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1103" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1103" type="surname" value="STAINS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1103" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH STAINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a painter. On the evening of the 28th of Feb. I was passing Mr. Higgs' shop—I observed the two prisoners standing together at the corner of his shop, and talking together, I believe, but I was not close enough to hear them—I passed a little way, then turned my head, and saw some person currying the roll of calico across the road under their arm.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184504070197"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Saville. Q.</hi> Why did you not immediately go to Mr. Higgs and tell him? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I did not know it was Mr. Higgs's—I had noticed the prisoners standing there, but I did not notice any calico as I passed.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450407-name-1104" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1104" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1104" type="surname" value="RAINER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1104" type="given" value="RACHEL"></interp>RACHEL RAINER</persName>
                  </hi>. I deal in marine stores, and live at Stratford, opposite Mr. Higgs. On the 28th of Feb. the prisoners came to my shop between seven and eight o'clock in the evening, and asked me to buy a roll of calico—I would not have anything to do with it—they then asked me to lend them a bag to put it in—I declined—they threw the roll of calico into the yard, I believe, but I did not see it—they left the roller in our yard—I saw it that night—I did not see it brought in the next morning, but I saw it on the fire, and the policeman came and took it out of the fire.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450407-name-1105" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1105" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1105" type="surname" value="POTTER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1105" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM POTTER</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 273.) I went to Rainer's and found the roller in the fire—I took it out and showed it to Mr. Jones, who identified it—I had taken the prisoners before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Lewis.</hi> When he took us he would not tell us what it was for; I did not know till I got to the station. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I did tell them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Saville.</hi> If it had been any other policeman they would have found the calico in Rainer's house; these policemen are drinking in her house when they ought to be on duty; she had been up here two or three times against boys for robbing.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">COURT</hi> to <hi rend="smallCaps">R. RAINER</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Why did you not go to Mr. Higgs's? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I was just putting my children to bed when I told the prisoners to take the calico away—I did not see it—it was on my premises a quarter of an hour—I could have gone to Mr. Higgs's—they had come and carried it off before my husband gave information.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450407-name-1106" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1106" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1106" type="surname" value="BENTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18450407-name-1106" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH BENTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable K</hi> 181.) I prodoce a certificate of Saville's former conviction, which I got at Mr. Clark's office—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted the Srd of Feb., 1845, and confined ten days</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">SAVILLE</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18450407-983-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
